    High-end doors to impress

    The Highline door series presents a new way of achieving the elegant and sophisticated look using the latest technology available. The Highline Series distinguishes itself amongst other series by the option to have it inlaid with wood mouldings. In turn, the same mouldings can be used in the adjacent wall and archway treatment. Worth mention, shaker design is the base for all Highline doors.
